{
  "stem": "3150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was worse than-- I mean, at that time, obviously, it was the-- it was great for us just to-- just to-- be-- just to live.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was-- the conditions was deplorable, I mean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that he made it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did everything he could.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it-- it was really-- he did everything he could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Petro Pawlotzki and his wife, I mean too-- and he really risked his life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He really risked his life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had contact with him after the-- so in fact, after World War I it was the-- when the Russian came back, that they used to pick up all-- they drafted all the men right away.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my brother went into the army too, at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- and-- and what they did, they also picked up a lot of women and sent them-- and sent them to work camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So his daughter was one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when-- when we-- we brought it to her house when we lived in Rowne already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she got a job, so they let-- they let her-- they did not send her away to-- to-- to work her.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we were there, we always had contact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had contacts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even when we live over here we send them packages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to send them most-- you know, they-- they would resell over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they both passed away already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were much older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, we had contact with them probably through early '80s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we would be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we had enough-- you know-- and really, we'd just sit and keep quiet and whisper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't really talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
